{"tid":1157131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大贏家又贏]日本理光公司決定由中國轉至泰國生產　避免受關稅影響","createTime":"2019-05-16T05:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T05:34:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":180,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"2aad8e7a459ca352eafcc66a49dc5a79558f0a07","tid":1157131,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"日本辦公室設備公司理光表示，已經決定將具有複印、打印等功能的複合機面向美國的生產，從中國全面轉移到泰國。<br />\n<br />\n理光的做法，相信是要避免受到美國對華加徵關稅影響，避免增加營運風險。複合機是美國對華加徵關稅第四批的對象，措施啟動時受影響的金額，可能達數十億日元。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公司由去年已開始準備轉移到泰國生產，若果落實的話，最快兩個月後可以從泰國出口。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n除了理光之外，三菱電機、小松、東芝機械等企業，去年已將部分生產從中國轉移至其他國家，卡西歐計算機也準備將鐘錶的生產，從中國轉移至泰國。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457826-20190516.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457826-20190516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=5363a86a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457826-20190516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8f403d10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457826-20190516.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ff0f5715f41eaf5d4f5318485466461dc191a493","tid":1157131,"uid":156363,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:15:37.000Z","msg":"泰國請一個工人要幾錢？大陸交足五險一金起碼5－6000RMB一個工人。"},{"pid":"66916b1447c2c0980d51af7b4ac382bdf9e9327e","tid":1157131,"uid":38546,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"又一間外國公司敗走，中國公司成本減低，中國又贏。"},{"pid":"6312515e79fe7dc1646ce469e109d92cbed9ebc9","tid":1157131,"uid":165782,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:48:41.000Z","msg":"成功驅逐軍國主義支持者的資金 又贏"},{"pid":"acda80bb92ee79372f617e7840fdaa4cc907e36a","tid":1157131,"uid":65346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":