l/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:12:56.000Z","msg":"我淨係知印尼班工人唔好得幾多，而且學野好慢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35db1024e880b1514245d1d1bd5b1c4d15cf3051","tid":1157131,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2aad8e7a459ca352eafcc66a49dc5a79558f0a07","tid":1157131,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"日本辦公室設備公司理光表示，已經決定將具有複印、打印等功能的複合機面向美國的生產，從中國全面轉移到泰國。<br />\n<br />\n理光的做法，相信是要避免受到美國對華加徵關稅影響，避免增加營運風險。複合機是美國對華加徵關稅第四批的對象，措施啟動時受影響的金額，可能達數十億日元。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公司由去年已開始準備轉移到泰國生產，若果落實的話，最快兩個月後可以從泰國出口。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n除了理光之外，三菱電機、小松、東芝機械等企業，去年已將部分生產從中國轉移至其他國家，卡西歐計算機也準備將鐘錶的生產，從中國轉移至泰國。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457826-20190516.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457826-20190516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=5363a86a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457826-20190516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8f403d10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457826-20190516.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>公司由去年已開始準備轉移到泰國生產，若果落實的話，最快兩個月後可以從泰國出口。<br />\n<br />\n公司由去年已開始準備轉移到泰國生產，若果落實的話，最快兩個月後可以從泰國出口。<br />\n<br />\n公司由去年已開始準備轉移到泰國生產，若果落實的話，最快兩個月後可以從泰國出口。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589108abd35e3417f076c73b84ea41f0a1aa8469","tid":1157131,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dis