7bd5f6d562abab63247aac","tid":1157131,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T23:11:28.000Z","msg":"中國民企市佔率又大升，贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6a48b637b58f886533398751d04e5f2160a575","tid":1157131,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T23:25:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">若然屬實 秦國可能成為最後贏家</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fe4ccd8d10726e9ed75a4716d922c57d9533d4","tid":1157131,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T23:33:13.000Z","msg":"ricoh d printer勁快壞 支那零件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b792c32b2b754837ef1c4289108a841a9a57099","tid":1157131,"uid":251736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2aad8e7a459ca352eafcc66a49dc5a79558f0a07","tid":1157131,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"日本辦公室設備公司理光表示，已經決定將具有複印、打印等功能的複合機面向美國的生產，從中國全面轉移到泰國。<br />\n<br />\n理光的做法，相信是要避免受到美國對華加徵關稅影響，避免增加營運風險。複合機是美國對華加徵關稅第四批的對象，措施啟動時受影響的金額，可能達數十億日元。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公司由去年已開始準備轉移到泰國生產，若果落實的話，最快兩個月後可以從泰國出口。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n除了理光之外，三菱電機、小松、東芝機械等企業，去年已將部分生產從中國轉移至其他國家，卡西歐計算機也準備將鐘錶的生產，從中國轉移至泰國。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457826-20190516.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457826-20190516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=5363a86a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457826-20190516.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8f403d10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457826-20190516.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T23:42:11.000Z","msg":"把生產線移到國外有助釋放勞動力，減少中國對製造業的依賴，促進多元及高科技的發展。<br />\n中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144a1b5d3593089797c52f1083a70f5a77e9966d","tid":1157131,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T23:43:11.000Z","msg":"日本敗走企業 贏贏贏！"}]}